sequenceDiagram
	autonumber
	participant CRON as Scheduler
	participant W as Ingestion Worker
	participant APIX as Mandi APIs
	participant M as MongoDB
	participant R as Redis
	participant WS as Socket.IO

	CRON->>W: Trigger every 15 min
	W->>R: SET kmb:lock:ingestion:prices worker1 EX 600 NX

	alt Lock denied
		R-->>W: null
		W-->>CRON: skip run (leader exists)
	else Lock acquired
		R-->>W: OK
		W->>APIX: GET mandi prices (HTTPS/JSON)
		APIX-->>W: raw prices
		W->>W: normalize + validate
		W->>M: bulkWrite mandiPrices (Mongo wire)
		W->>R: HSET kmb:price:latest:* + EXPIRE 900
		W->>W: compute delta + anomaly
		W->>R: XADD kmb:stream:price:events anomaly payload
		W->>WS: broadcast price:anomaly + price:update
		W->>M: upsert priceSnapshots
		W->>R: DEL kmb:lock:ingestion:prices
		W-->>CRON: success metrics
	end

